text: (achchha aur lo) apana haath garebaan mein daalo (aur nikaal lo) to saphed burraaq hokar beaib nikal aaya aur khauph kee (vajah) se apane baajoo apanee taraph samet lo (taaki khauph jaata rahe) garaz ye donon (asa va yade baiza) tumhaare paravaradigaar kee taraph se (tumhaaree nuboovat kee) do daleelen phiraun aur usake darabaar ke saradaaron ke vaaste hain aur isamen shak nahin ki vah badakaar log the
